@yield @code4rena I've judged now about half a dozen contests and know how wardens score cheap shots. I want them to spend their time in higher value analysis.

So we went through past reports, preempted them, and then thoroughly documented design decisions.

A+++ would preempt again.

@the_ethernaut We tried with @yield v1, and I tried again with @usmfum. Building a 100% permissionless product is insanely hard.

It needs to be very simple, probably just one use case, and you need to hit your market with your first shot.

Progressive decentralisation sounds more realistic.

